nodes.text: Tun'sa Nem'ro was an individual who resided on the planet Nal Hutta during the war between the First Order and the Resistance. An All Terrain Armored Transport targeting computer was registered to Nem'ro's name.

Tun'sa Nem'ro was first mentioned in Star Wars: Datapad, a mobile game companion to the theme park Star Wars: Galaxy's Edge. Nem'ro shares their name with Suudaa Nem'ro, a Hutt crime lord who appeared in the 2011 video game Star Wars: The Old Republic.
